00:10:05.940 --> 00:10:08.850
and whether you can just
get away with a web client

00:10:08.850 --> 00:10:10.580
when the right time
is to go native.

00:10:10.580 --> 00:10:13.960
Do you have any strong
feelings about that?

00:10:13.960 --> 00:10:16.420
So I'm going to ask you
last, because actually I

00:10:16.420 --> 00:10:18.510
think-- actually I'll ask
you first on this one,

00:10:18.510 --> 00:10:22.070
because you'll sit very clearly
on one side of the equation,

00:10:22.070 --> 00:10:22.770
I suspect.

00:10:22.770 --> 00:10:24.061
RYAN BATEMAN: Yeah, I mean yes.

00:10:24.061 --> 00:10:26.250
