00:10:26.250 --> 00:10:27.910
I think there are
certainly occasions

00:10:27.910 --> 00:10:33.160
where hybrid applications
or web applications are

00:10:33.160 --> 00:10:35.830
a good solution.

00:10:35.830 --> 00:10:40.685
