yes, yes, and yes.

00:11:11.280 --> 00:11:15.980
So, yeah, Kevin and I
have this discussion.

00:11:15.980 --> 00:11:21.260
And there are always
situations where

00:11:21.260 --> 00:11:27.990
a hybrid-- that's a nice name--
a hybrid application makes

00:11:27.990 --> 00:11:28.490
sense.

00:11:28.490 --> 00:11:30.530
