where, quite frankly,

00:11:30.530 --> 00:11:33.940
the user has no option, right?

00:11:33.940 --> 00:11:35.430
It's an educational app.

00:11:35.430 --> 00:11:38.630
There's a specific
budget requirement.

00:11:38.630 --> 00:11:40.260
