underneath the hood,

00:13:01.580 --> 00:13:03.940
is the same damn thing twice.

00:13:03.940 --> 00:13:08.510
And as you're maintaining
it over the course of months

00:13:08.510 --> 00:13:13.770
and years, you get
even copy/paste errors.

00:13:13.770 --> 00:13:16.790
And those things have to be
tracked down, and that cost,

00:13:16.790 --> 00:13:19.680
that's a real cost.

00:13:19.680 --> 00:13:21.680
There are some good solutions.

00:13:25.470 --> 00:13:30.350
There may be a much better
solution on the horizon,

00:13:30.350 --> 00:13:33.050
and that's all I'll
say about that.

00:13:33.050 --> 00:13:34.550
But it is the challenge.

00:13:34.550 --> 00:13:38.120
But there is no
comparison to native

00:13:38.120 --> 00:13:39.687
when it comes to quality.

00:13:39.687 --> 00:13:41.270
RUPERT WHITEHEAD:
It's interesting you

00:13:41.270 --> 00:13:43.870
