native-like experience

00:13:55.530 --> 00:13:57.720
but purely using
web technologies

00:13:57.720 --> 00:14:00.340
rather than, I'd say,
the hybrid web-view apps,

00:14:00.340 --> 00:14:04.660
which is a slightly
different case.

00:14:04.660 --> 00:14:07.251
JEFF NAMNUM: Yeah,
doing a thing, yeah.

00:14:07.251 --> 00:14:09.750
PRADEEP NALLURI: We do have a
