the iOS side, your customer,

00:14:52.380 --> 00:14:54.060
or they come from
the Android side.

00:14:54.060 --> 00:14:56.694
And they seem to believe
that one size fits all.

00:14:56.694 --> 00:14:59.110
I think you're kind of nodding
