design that's much more

00:18:04.380 --> 00:18:06.260
native to the platform.

00:18:06.260 --> 00:18:08.340
And that's-- yeah,
it does depend.

00:18:08.340 --> 00:18:12.660
I think that you can't
do that all the time.

00:18:12.660 --> 00:18:15.640
But if all the arguments
fail, it's easier

00:18:15.640 --> 00:18:19.386
just to pull in five random
people and say, yeah,

00:18:19.386 --> 00:18:21.402
this is our expert witness.

00:18:21.402 --> 00:18:23.610
PRADEEP NALLURI: In the past
