00:18:58.350 --> 00:19:03.090
But if you were going to give
one tip to the other agencies

00:19:03.090 --> 00:19:05.690
here, something you
found useful internally

00:19:05.690 --> 00:19:08.060
within your own
company, that you

00:19:08.060 --> 00:19:12.010
found a way of doing things that
maybe is not hugely well-known

00:19:12.010 --> 00:19:15.570
